===Formula One records and achievements===

* On 3 October 2014, Verstappen became the youngest driver to participate in a Formula One Grand Prix weekend (17 years, 3 days), driving in FP1 at the [[2014 Japanese Grand Prix|Japanese Grand Prix]], deputising in place of Toro Rosso's Jean-Eric Vergne.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Max Verstappen Q&A: I was in full 'safe' mode for debut run |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/interviews/2014/10/Max-Verstappen-Q%26A-I-was-in-full-safe-mode-for-debut-run.html |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210908180111/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/interviews/2014/10/Max-Verstappen-Q%26A-I-was-in-full-safe-mode-for-debut-run.html |archive-date=8 September 2021 |access-date=8 September 2021 |publisher=Formula One}}</ref>
* On 3 August 2019, Verstappen became the first [[Formula One drivers from the Netherlands|Dutch Formula One driver]] to take pole position, doing so at the [[2019 Hungarian Grand Prix|Hungarian Grand Prix]], while also becoming the 100th polesitter in the sport's history.<ref>{{cite web |date=3 August 2019 |title=Max Verstappen pakt eerste pole position uit carrière |trans-title=Max Verstappen takes first career pole position |url=https://www.hartvannederland.nl/nieuws/2019/max-verstappen-pakt-eerste-pole-position-uit-carriere/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803222328/https://www.hartvannederland.nl/nieuws/2019/max-verstappen-pakt-eerste-pole-position-uit-carriere/ |archive-date=3 August 2019 |access-date=4 August 2019 |publisher=[[:nl:Hart van Nederland]] |language=nl}}</ref>
* On 23 May 2021, Verstappen became the first Dutch Formula One driver to lead the World Championship after winning the [[2021 Monaco Grand Prix|Monaco Grand Prix]].<ref>{{cite web |author=Noud Bemelen and Rik Spekenbrink |date=23 May 2021 |title=Historische dubbelslag: Verstappen wint GP van Monaco en is eerste Nederlandse WK-leider ooit |trans-title=Historic double: Verstappen wins Monaco GP and is the first Dutch leader of the world championship ever |url=https://www.ad.nl/formule-1/historische-dubbelslag-verstappen-wint-gp-van-monaco-en-is-eerste-nederlandse-wk-leider-ooit~a06b2fb0/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523195919/https://www.ad.nl/formule-1/historische-dubbelslag-verstappen-wint-gp-van-monaco-en-is-eerste-nederlandse-wk-leider-ooit~a06b2fb0/ |archive-date=23 May 2021 |access-date=23 May 2021 |publisher=[[:nl:AD]] |language=nl}}</ref>

